songs.title: Fresh Prince Theme
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Yeah, yeah!

[Verse]
Now this is a story all about me
A young Asian rapping acting MC
Here's the weekly 16s voted by you dudes
I tell you how a became the prince of a site called Youtube
On the East side of long beach I lived till I was 10
Then I moved to paramount, that's where the story begins
Black kids called me Jin, Mexicans called me Chino
The 10 Asian kids thought I was Filipino
They heard I could rap, so we battled at lunchtime
I gained a reputation as the Asian with punchlines
Bootlegging CD's making money
Prom king, class clown, yea I've always been funny
I linked with PDFlo and SupereeeGO then we started
Making silly movies, some of em were mad retarded
Got Ricky Shucks to finish up the team
Loaded up the cameras and started chasing our dreams
Then I found Youtube uploaded some dumb shit
A few people watched then a couple of hundreds
But I'mma stay grinding like behind a girl
'Cuz fuck Youtube, I'm tryna be rule the world

[Outro]
Yeah! That's me baby
The Fresh Prince reincarnated
Timothy DeLaGhetto
I get my name from Fresh Prince if you don't know that
